# 🏦 Sextant FX Dashboard

## FX & Liquidity Simulation Module

The Sextant FX Dashboard is a deterministic simulation layer for modeling foreign exchange dynamics, liquidity flow, and cross-border financial stress propagation within the Sextant resilience system.

