## 🧠 System Functions

- FX rate simulation (synthetic)
- Liquidity flow propagation
- Cross-currency stress modeling
- Bank exposure sensitivity mapping
- Macro shock transmission effects

---

## 🏦 Simulation Layer

The system models:

- Currency dependency networks  
- Regional liquidity constraints  
- FX shock amplification  
- Multi-node financial coupling  

---

## ⚠ System Classification

- Simulation-only system  
- No real financial execution  
- No market connectivity  
- No banking integration  
- Deterministic synthetic outputs only  

